<tableCitation box="[884,965,1816,1840]" captionStart="Table 1" captionStartId="8.[515,571,248,269]" captionText="Table 1 Leg setation and solenidia of adultHardybodes minutus n. sp." pageId="3" pageNumber="133">Table 1</tableCitation>
. Famulus of tarsi short, erect, blunt-ended, inserted proximal to ω 
<subScript attach="left" box="[640,649,1863,1880]" fontSize="7" pageId="3" pageNumber="133">1</subScript>
